  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate over the 24 month prospective follow up - in
      everyday clinical practice - resource utilization and effectiveness of the treatment of
      acromegalic patients in Poland with Somatuline Autogel 120 mg including extended injection
      intervals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
